{"ANALYTE": ["THC", "CBD"]}

The patient's symptoms resolved within 24 hours with supportive care and no specific treatment. This case highlights the importance of proper dosing and monitoring of patients using medicinal cannabis, particularly those with a history of substance abuse or other health conditions.

